title: HP on the Shapes of Things to Come for 3D printing
text:
Expand HP's Scott Schiller at TCT Show The first video in our TCT Show + Personalize 2015 Conference series comes from our keynote sessions on the opening day as J. Scott Schiller, Worldwide Director 3D Printing, Hewlett-Packard gives a keynote presentation to share the story and vision of what will soon become one of the biggest players in the 3D space thanks to its Multi Jet Fusion technology. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel. Tags
